# nested-prefix-missing-outer-close

## Input

```
a {
  b {
    c 1
  }

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..22
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..22
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    SPACE@4..6 "  "
    PREFIX_BLOCK@6..22
      WORD_KEY@6..7
        WORD@6..7 "b"
      SPACE@7..8 " "
      OPEN_BRACE@8..9 "{"
      NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
      SPACE@10..14 "    "
      ENTRY@14..18
        WORD_KEY@14..15
          WORD@14..15 "c"
        SPACE@15..16 " "
        INTEGER@16..17
          NUMERAL@16..17 "1"
        NEWLINE@17..18 "\n"
      SPACE@18..20 "  "
      CLOSE_BRACE@20..21 "}"
      NEWLINE@21..22 "\n"
```

## Syntax Error

```
[
    SyntaxError {
        message: "missing closing '}' for prefix block",
        range: 22..22,
    },
]
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{",
            items: [
                PrefixBlock {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@6..7 "b",
                    },
                    open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@8..9 "{",
                    items: [
                        Entry {
                            key: WordKey {
                                word: WORD@14..15 "c",
                            },
                            value: Integer {
                                sign: none,
                                numeral: NUMERAL@16..17 "1",
                            },
                        },
                    ],
                    close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@20..21 "}",
                },
            ],
            close_brace: none,
        },
    ],
}
```

